<section id="subversion-intro">
<title>Introduction</title>

<para><ulink url="http://subversion.tigris.org">Subversion</ulink> is a
version control system that is intended to supersede 
<ulink url="https://www.cvshome.org">CVS</ulink>.  Some of the features of
Subversion are:
</para>

<para><itemizedList>
<listItem><para>Supports moves</para></listItem>
<listItem><para>Multiple authentication options</para></listItem>
<listItem><para>Branches and tags are implemented as "cheap" copies</para></listItem>
<listItem><para>Metadata (or properties) can be added to files and directories</para></listItem>
</itemizedList>
</para>

<para>For more information about Subversion, see the following
documentation:</para>

